Package: canvasser
Title: Scrape and calculate grades from Canvas
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Brandon",
           family = "Tat",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bjtat@calpoly.edu"),
    person(given = "Kelly",
            family = "Bodwin",
            role = "aut"))
Description: Allows user to scrape data from Canvas Learning Managment System; 
    including assignment grades, grade breakdowns, course averages, and course totals. 
    The data can be pulled from a HTML page but it is recommended to download the 
    HTML file onto your local computer then run the data scraping on it. 
